data.description: Remarkable Investment Opportunity in the Heart of Miami! for both investors and homeowners! Located in the up and coming neighborhood of Allapattah.  Enjoy the proximity to various amenities and attractions that make it truly desirable, such as The beautiful River Landing Mall, Miami River, Wynwood, The Shops at Midtown & Miami Design District, South Beach and the famous Calle 8, which are just a few minutes away. For added convenience, Jackson Memorial Hospital, the University of Miami Hospital I-95 and Miami International Airport are just mins away as well.  Walking distance to Allapattah Metro rail station.  NO HOA!!!  SOLD AS IS!!!
